    "In mobile networks, ML helps analyze and optimize the use of frequencies to avoid interference and maximize coverage [97].",
    "ConclusionNFV promises operating expenditure savings and high flexibility in managing networks.",
    "However, some challenges still need to be overcome, namely for resource allocation, security and anomaly detection.",
    "In this paper, we discussed the potential of ML to overcome these problems.",
    "We included a survey of existing contributions and highlighted some opportunities and research directions."
  ]
